#title "Isaiah xiii, 1-3"

The burden of Babylon, which Isaiah the son of Amoz saw: "Lift up a banner upon the high mountain; exalt the voice unto them, shake the hand, that they may go into the gates of the nobles. I have commanded My sanctified ones; I have also called My mighty ones for My anger, even them who rejoice in My highness."

